@startuml
title Metric containers - semantic dependency graph (containers + derived metrics)

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

' --- Containers (producers) ---
package "Metric Containers (Docker)" {
  [ce-ca-jdepend\n(metrics/coupling/java/ce-ca-jdepend)] as C_JDEPEND
  [ce-ca-ck-cbo\n(metrics/coupling/java/ce-ca-ck-cbo)] as C_CK_CBO

  [lcom-ckjm\n(metrics/cohesion/java/lcom-ckjm)] as C_LCOM_CKJM
  [lcom-ck\n(metrics/cohesion/java/lcom-ck)] as C_LCOM_CK

  [cc-ckjm\n(metrics/complexity/java/cc-ckjm)] as C_CC_CKJM
  [cc-lizard\n(metrics/complexity/generic/cc-lizard)] as C_CC_LIZARD
  [cc-radon\n(metrics/complexity/python/cc-radon)] as C_CC_RADON

  [loc-cloc\n(metrics/**/loc-cloc)] as C_LOC_CLOC
  [loc-tokei\n(metrics/**/loc-tokei)] as C_LOC_TOKEI

  [halstead-javancss\n(metrics/volume/java/halstead-javancss)] as C_HAL_JAVANCSS
  [halstead-radon\n(metrics/volume/python/halstead-radon)] as C_HAL_RADON

  [churn-git\n(metrics/evolution/generic/churn-git)] as C_CHURN_GIT

  [duplication-jscpd\n(metrics/duplication/java/duplication-jscpd)] as C_DUP_JSCPD
}

' --- Normalized data layer ---
database "Normalized\nresults_normalized/*.jsonl" as D_NORM

' --- Analysis / Derived metrics ---
package "Derived Metrics (Analysis)" {
  [Instability\nI = Ce / (Ca + Ce)] as M_INSTABILITY
  [Abstractness\nA = Na / Nc] as M_ABSTRACTNESS
  [Distance from Main\nD = |A + I - 1|] as M_DISTANCE
}

' --- Producers -> normalized layer (conceptual) ---
C_JDEPEND --> D_NORM : produces Ca, Ce (+ packages)
C_CK_CBO --> D_NORM : produces coupling variants
C_LCOM_CKJM --> D_NORM
C_LCOM_CK --> D_NORM
C_CC_CKJM --> D_NORM
C_CC_LIZARD --> D_NORM
C_CC_RADON --> D_NORM
C_LOC_CLOC --> D_NORM
C_LOC_TOKEI --> D_NORM
C_HAL_JAVANCSS --> D_NORM
C_HAL_RADON --> D_NORM
C_CHURN_GIT --> D_NORM
C_DUP_JSCPD --> D_NORM

' --- Derived dependencies ---
D_NORM --> M_INSTABILITY : needs Ca, Ce
D_NORM --> M_ABSTRACTNESS : needs Na, Nc (if available)
M_INSTABILITY --> M_DISTANCE
M_ABSTRACTNESS --> M_DISTANCE

note right of M_INSTABILITY
Instability is typically derived from afferent/efferent coupling:
- Ca (Afferent coupling)
- Ce (Efferent coupling)

If your pipeline stores Ca/Ce from JDepend in normalized output,
you can compute Instability in analysis/build_dataset.py or a dedicated step.
end note

@enduml